Text: Great song from one of my favourite bands.
My favorite is "Dum Dum Girl, i love the bass sound that starts 17 seconds into the song, and then again at 1:20 seconds :)

I Believe in You is another awesome song, as is It's My Life.

Mark Hollis has an incredible voice.
Talk Talk / Mark  Hollis is fantastic. Thanks for the uploads. You should check Talk Talk live in Montreux also. A brilliant concert with some great live-versions.
I've noticed some audio/video out of sync issues with this video, but it does play fine sometimes so it might just be my pc '.'
